              \(princ \":FUNCTION `mon-string-split-dir-recurse' errored\"\)\)\n
\(when \(and \(intern-soft \"*mon-ebay-images-bmp-path*\"\) 
           \(bound-and-true-p *mon-ebay-images-bmp-path*\)\) 
